{"tid":1878709,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"經濟艙起革命    新座位設計感覺似商務！","createTime":"2020-02-13T18:41:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T03:36:45.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ff4ea5058b70a2348b938cfc2e6f7e7572c7b389","tid":1878709,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T18:41:24.000Z","msg":"坐飛機從來都唔係令人享受嘅事，除非你係坐商務或者頭等艙；畢竟經濟艙又逼又窄，幾乎要掂住隔離位一樣，更談不上任何私人空間。不過日前有公司就專為經濟艙設計出一種新式座位名為「Interspace」，最大特色係座位背兩邊可以用手拉出靠墊，包圍住自己兩邊，唔單止可以畀乘客挨住休息、睡眠；同時仲形成一個小小個人空間，包圍住自己。座位用碳纖維製，重量好輕，好易拉出，而且唔會導致飛機重量增加。有此設計，全賴設計師Luke Miles，佢曾經於維珍航空任職座位設計總工程師3年之久，佢發現航空公司一般只會盡力設計如何令商務、頭等艙變得更舒適，反而最多人坐嘅經濟艙卻無投入任何人力去研究改善，因此佢先構思改革經驗艙座位，希望可以令旅客唔再視坐飛機係苦事，可以享受坐飛機嘅時間。不過暫時Luke Miles未公佈佢向邊啲航空公司推銷緊Interspace，因為畢竟要徹底更換經濟艙所有座位，都係一件相當費時費成本嘅事，未知會否有航空公司願意改革呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_v2.E5bLJXeBqGD7s_c_EQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjUyO2g9MzY3/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-02/0081faa0-4e2b-11ea-beff-89d67bfbdbd7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F_v2.E5bLJXeBqGD7s_c_EQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjUyO2g9MzY3%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-02%2F0081faa0-4e2b-11ea-beff-89d67bfbdbd7&h=3e05119f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nInterspace設計用上碳纖維，唔會增加飛機總載重量。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/E6T7eQqH67wIk..kTMgimA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjUyO2g9MzY3/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-02/06fbd8b0-4e2b-11ea-bf7d-b91134dfc984\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FE6T7eQqH67wIk..kTMgimA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjUyO2g9MzY3%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-02%2F06fbd8b0-4e2b-11ea-bf7d-b91134dfc984&h=81190b1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n座位可將兩邊拉出，成為一對翼包圍自己。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/6V4pqkU5WJPYQ10YAxKbtQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTkzO2g9Mjg0/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-02/0c624af0-4e2b-11ea-aaaf-5ec981d1c4dd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F6V4pqkU5WJPYQ10YAxKbtQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTkzO2g9Mjg0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-02%2F0c624af0-4e2b-11ea-aaaf-5ec981d1c4dd&h=6e0c101a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n經濟艙大改革，望落尤如商務艙一樣咁舒適！"},{"pid":"ee51843c19c25e18fa0f4926d6ea848e615d37fb","tid":1878709,"uid":38164,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T20:31:55.000Z","msg":"一直覺得太薄身唔舒服"},{"pid":"34f47f14f31a78bf612b14c7bca1b4dbf6f8d1a2","tid":1878709,"uid":10524,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ff4ea5058b70a2348b938cfc2e6f7e7572c7b389","tid":1878709,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T18:41:24.000Z","msg":"坐飛機從來都唔係令人享受嘅事，除非你係坐商務或者頭等艙；畢竟經濟艙又逼又窄，幾乎要掂住隔離位一樣，更談不上任何私人空間。不過日前有公司就專為經濟艙設計出一種新式座位名為「Interspace」，最大特色係座位背兩邊可以用手拉出靠墊，包圍住自己兩邊，唔單止可以畀乘客挨住休息、睡眠；同時仲形成一個小小個人空間，包圍住自己。座位用碳纖維製，重量好輕，好易拉出，而且唔會導致飛機重量增加。有此設計，全賴設計師Luke Miles，佢曾經於維珍航空任職座位設計總工程師3年之久，佢發現航空公司一般只會盡力設計如何令商務、頭等艙變得更舒適，反而最多人坐嘅經濟艙卻無投入任何人力去研究改善，因此佢先構思改革經驗艙座位，希望可以令旅客唔再視坐飛機係苦事，可以享受坐飛機嘅時間。不過暫時Luke Miles未公佈佢向邊啲航空公司推銷緊Interspace，因為畢竟要徹底更換經濟艙所有座位，都係一件相當費時費成本嘅事，未知會否有航空公司願意改革呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/_v2.E5bLJXeBqGD7s_c_EQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjUyO2g9MzY3/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-02/0081faa0-4e2b-11ea-beff-89d67bfbdbd7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F_v2.E5bLJXeBqGD7s_c_EQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjUyO2g9MzY3%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-02%2F0081faa0-4e2b-11ea-